spec_data.Name: perl-Config-Extend-MySQL
spec_data.Description:
This module extends other Config:: modules so they can read MySQL
configuration files. It works by slurping and preprocessing the files
before letting your favorite Config:: module parse the result.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:21:33 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Extend your favorite .INI parser module to read MySQL configuration file
